        Email us for any questions or check our FAQs for quick answers.
      </p>
      <a
        href="/childcare-centre-faqs/"
        class="inline-flex py-2 px-4 text-sm font-medium text-center rounded-lg border text-little-lens-green-600 border-little-lens-green-600 hover:text-little-lens-green-800 hover:bg-little-lens-green-200 focus:ring-4 focus:outline-none focus:little-lens-green-300"
